{
  "texts": [
    "In addition to ensuring the security of the physical layer, AI is expected to enhance the security of the higher layers of ISAC networks.",
    "For example, by leveraging its powerful data analysis capabilities, AI can be used to detect the insider attacks [272].",
    "However, the AI-enabled secure ISAC has not been well studied, and how to achieve cross-layer secure design for ISAC networks with the help of AI is an interesting but challenging problem.",
    "GAI-enabled ISACRecently, GAI has become a hot topic in the field of AI due to its powerful context generation capabilities, resulting in some groundbreaking applications such as ChatGPT and SORA.",
    "Thanks to its generation capabilities, GAI can be used to generate huge training samples, improving the training efficiency of the AI model, especially when real-world samples are limited or collecting sufficient samples is timeconsuming and expensive."
  ]
}